        </div>
        <div class="case-card">
          <p class="co">not traditional consulting</p>
          <p>The deck-then-depart model ends exactly where the difficulty begins. I stay through implementation, and my proof points are systems still running years later — a claim the slide-deck model structurally cannot make.</p>
        </div>
